{"tid":1617352,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS Whatsapp個backup真係究極ON9","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:59:03.000Z","uid":9777,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"44fd30b60ef5b446e6845749d4597d0612588bfa","tid":1617352,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n用上台累積嘅優惠卷拎咗部XR走<br />\n<br />\n之前無買i Cloud 一直無back up<br />\n想將部舊6s whatsapp backup<br />\n點知佢話手機無位<br />\n買撚完iCloud<br />\n都係話無位 一定要清部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後諗住XR同步晒啲相就開始係6s del 相<br />\n竟然同我連icould嘅都del 撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果阻止唔切連iPad 同XR都一齊DEL咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌那聲 我都唔知怪自己ON9定咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想認真問 點樣先可以令機自己del嘢唔連iCloud一齊DEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04845db17d4d833e04d98e5392deeb602032f5b","tid":1617352,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"順便問 有無iPhone救相程式推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a585e23ee6e5e6ac9a9254731d758eed50d3c4","tid":1617352,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"唔該各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"2aaf905f2deaf89d3ba12b30a3ca85db8f23af41","tid":1617352,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到黑警慘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e15fd2d2ae853587ae20c4c9f03dacd25110844","tid":1617352,"uid":80179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"唔買iCloud就係罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800368a38418605f0cb14b188bfd6aa50b4db02b","tid":1617352,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e15fd2d2ae853587ae20c4c9f03dacd25110844","tid":1617352,"uid":80179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"唔買iCloud就係罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:04:10.000Z","msg":"講起就嬲<br />\n比撚完錢買<br />\n就有死Gay Cook奶共post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n激撚死我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a217a876d63f235ab705e3fab10c775390dfacd3","tid":1617352,"uid":30347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vfLwzXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvfLwzXn.png&h=9b68b801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你買完位之後有冇駁Wi-Fi，再手動backup?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2